message: To consistently get 100 points, always start by using the 'vial' tool on a solid magical ingredient (like unicorn horn, mandrake root, dragon scale) to create a magical extract. Then, use the 'vial' tool on a solid mundane ingredient (like obsidian, mushroom, dandelion, rose petal, amber, bat wing) to create a mundane extract. Finally, combine these two extracts (magical + mundane) to achieve a score of 100. Be cautious with liquid and gas ingredients, as applying the vial to them often results in negative values ('failed extraction'). The 'filter' tool and combining negative items did not consistently lead to high scores in my experience, so prioritize the solid-extract-combination strategy.
